WEBVTT

00:08:59.188 --> 00:09:01.428
osetite pesak pod stopalima,

00:09:01.442 --> 00:09:02.593
prošetate do okeana

00:09:02.627 --> 00:09:04.740
i dopustite da vam okean zapljusne članke.

00:09:05.207 --> 00:09:07.826
Vaš život će biti bogatiji i smisleniji

00:09:07.826 --> 00:09:10.264
zato što ste uneli u sebe to iskustvo

00:09:10.288 --> 00:09:12.684
i zato što ste ostavili telefon u autu.

00:09:12.708 --> 00:09:13.879
Hvala.

00:09:13.903 --> 00:09:15.544
(Aplauz)